About
Anchored by more than 15 flagship stores, including Louis Vuitton, Gucci, Dolce & Gabbana, Tom Ford, Prada, Celine, Fendi and Tiffany & Co., The Shops at Crystals is an amazing collection of 50 of the finest luxury brands in the world, all under one roof. The gorgeous architecture, convenient location on the Las Vegas Boulevard, and exclusive luxury retailer lineup, make The Shops at Crystals a must-see for any visitor.
Duration: 2-3 hours

Same Stores As Many Other Places
Oct 2024 • Friends
Our friends wanted to see these shops. We all agreed it was like walking into the same shops as we had seen already at
the Encore and Caesars. Even the goods in the windows were very similar. All very high end and very empty on the Monday afternoon we went.

We took the monorail from the Bellagio so it was convenient. My friend told me this was the biggest Louis Vuitton store in the USA so we wanted to see it.

He had a bad experience there in July He was staying at the Encore and went over to the Crystal shops. It was his wife’s birthday and she found a jacket she wanted. She needed a different size and the sales woman said she could get it sent over from another store soon. He waited, no jacket, they went to lunch came back still no jacket. Went out browsing, still no jacket. After several hours he asked where it was. The woman said it was coming from the Encore and there were delivery delays. He was staying at the Encore !! She wanted the commission and didn’t give a damn about their time or convenience. This is greed at its worst !! It finally arrived. I told him he should have insisted he pick it up at the Encore. My word for people like this is slugs !!
Written October 25, 2024

Horrible Customer Service - I have to spend more money to fix THEIR issue!
Oct 2023
I was sold a damaged bottle of cologne when in Las Vegas at the Shops at Crystals. The lid was badly damaged and needs to be replaced. I reached out numerous times via phone, chat, and email all to be told that I have to go into a store to have the issue resolved. I don't know why a lid can't be shipped to me in the mail!!! I will never buy from Louis Vuitton again!!

Great Shopping!
Dec 2023 • Family
This is an indoor mall of luxury designers. It is 2 floors and the mall is on the smaller side. Some of the stores include Gucci, LV, Prada, Chanel, Hermes, Fendi, Alice and Olivia, Bottega, Loub, and Harry Winston. Google the mall to see the full list of stores. There is a bathroom and elevator but for food we went next door to Aria. You open the door to leave the Crystals mall and walk a few feet then open the door to enter Aria. It was very close.
